Package: hetzner-vrrp-failover
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3.11, python3-yaml, python3-hcloud
Description: Hetzner Cloud VRRP failover script for VyOS
 This package provides a script to manage Hetzner Cloud floating IPs and
 alias IPs during VRRP failover events on VyOS routers. It automatically
 reassigns floating IPs to the active VRRP master and configures alias IPs
 on the system interface.
